{
  "stem": "3022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I got the job in the physical lab for testing metals.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This particular engineer, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Push, ?] was responsible for saving several Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He had a young man by name of Ernst Noble working in his chemical lab.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And one time-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One of the interns, German intern who was there for the summer, out of just spite or fun, shot Ernst Noble to the leg.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And normally, that meant execution, because you were not any more able to perform work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Engineer [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Push ?] made sure that Ernst Noble was not executed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was kept in a dispensary, and saved his life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "On another occasion, an elderly Jew by the name of Reichman, who did not survive, but his three sons survived and lived in, in New York after, after the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He worked in the facility where they had cyanide baths.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In order to form the aluminum for-- to shape it, you had to give it a bath in the hot cyanide bath, so it became pliable.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And one of these-- this particular Jewish man, he did something that ruined some material, and he was slated to be executed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And General-- Engineer [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Push ?] got on a bicycle, went to the killing grounds in [INAUDIBLE], and threatened the, the, the gestapo, that if they execute this particular man, he's going to shut down the department.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he brought that man home, saved his life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He, he nurtured myself and another fellow who worked in the x-ray.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He used to bring us food, and he used to bring us eggs, and we used to fry them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we used to fry them in the x-ray department.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We used to put the red lights on that we were, you know, was doing some work.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
